{"word":"G3403 - μιμνήσκω - mimnḗskō - mim-nace'-ko - Be mindful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μιμνήσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mimnḗskō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mim-nace'-ko</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be mindful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நினை, நினைத்துக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"to remind"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A prolonged form of <a href=\"#/G3415 - μνάομαι - mnáomai - mnah'-om-ahee/3415\">G3415</a> (from which some of the tenses are borrowed); to <i>remind</i>, that is, (middle voice) to <i>recall to mind:</i> - be mindful, remember.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3403/3403\">G3403</a>, <a href=\"#/G3417/3417\">G3417</a>, <a href=\"#/G3418/3418\">G3418</a>, <a href=\"#/G3419/3419\">G3419</a>, <a href=\"#/G3420/3420\">G3420</a>, <a href=\"#/G3421/3421\">G3421</a>, <a href=\"#/G3422/3422\">G3422</a>"}]}